org.hkijena.jipipe.extensions.plots.datatypes

Class StatisticalCategoryPlotData

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hkijena.jipipe.extensions.plots.datatypes.PlotData
      • org.hkijena.jipipe.extensions.plots.datatypes.CategoryPlotData
        • org.hkijena.jipipe.extensions.plots.datatypes.StatisticalCategoryPlotData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JIPipeData, JIPipeValidatable, JIPipeParameterCollection
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BarStatisticalCategoryPlotData, LineStatisticalCategoryPlotData

    public abstract class StatisticalCategoryPlotData
extends CategoryPlotData
    Contains data for statistical plots. Generates StatisticalCategoryDataset. Any category plot has following columns: Value (Double), Category (String), Group (String)

    Values are assigned a category that is its X-axis. Colors are assigned by its group
